howToSwitchRoleAnswer:
## üîÑ Switching Your Role

In the app, you can choose between two roles:

### üë§ User  
As a **User**, you can:
- Create service orders
- Wait for freelancers to make offers
- Choose the best offer that fits your needs

### üßë‚Äçüíº Freelancer  
As a **Freelancer**, you can:
- View available service requests
- Make offers to complete jobs
- Earn money when you successfully finish an order

### üîÅ Switching Roles  
Use the toggle switch on the **home screen** to switch your role anytime you want.
howToManageServicesAnswer:
## üß∞ Managing Your Services

Here‚Äôs what you can do after submitting a service:

### ‚ùå Cancel a Service  
You can cancel your service **if no one has submitted an offer yet**.

### üóëÔ∏è Delete  
You can delete any of your services at any time.

### ‚úèÔ∏è Edit  
You can **edit service details** such as title, price, description, or location after submitting.

### üìú View History  
You can view all your **previous services**, including:

You can also **delete** past services or choose to **repost** them again.
